<paragraph blockId="136.[151,1437,151,1653]" pageId="136" pageNumber="137">
<emphasis box="[199,273,225,248]" italics="true" pageId="136" pageNumber="137">Larva.</emphasis>
The larvae of 
<emphasis box="[454,647,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="136" pageNumber="137">
S. “ 
<taxonomicName box="[494,638,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Streblognathus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="136" pageNumber="137" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aethiopicus">aethiopicus</taxonomicName>
